    Megatron looked to Kitkat when Waspinator entered the cave. "Your in 
command until my return. I want you to get rid of those invaders....failure 
is not an option. I dont think I need to remind you. And tell Starscream if 
he wants to join he had better pick up a blaster and shoot someone!"
    He began to leave, but turned agian. "Waspinator, Atma, and Purseudo are 
under you command as well as the others. Use it wisely."
    He exited the cave and the fans slid out and he took to the sky heading 
from the predacon bunker.

    "When will he get here?!!" Tarantulas demanded to Aracnia.
    She turned to him, angry. "I dont know! But hes going to help us, despite 
what Quickstrike and Darkmouse say. He should be here soon."
    "Hah, so will the Aliens."
